g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYhWavU.jpg&h=be245948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5) &ldquo;Freedom is never voluntarily given by the oppressor; it must be demanded by the oppressed.&rdquo;  Martin Luther King Jr.<br />\n<br />\n美國民權人士馬丁路德金<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OYiRJSm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYiRJSm.jpg&h=d00ca78a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6) &ldquo;They who can give up essential liberty to obtain a little temporary safety deserve neither liberty nor safety.&rdquo; Benjamin Franklin<br />\n<br />\n美國開國元老富蘭克林<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uAeUGGd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuAeUGGd.jpg&h=704597f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後講句：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:25:07.000Z","msg":"鄺神慷慨激昂鬧狗頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QjYycQ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQjYycQ7.png&h=52c7969c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HSXyXhO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHSXyXhO.png&h=ec5e7b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H38RJXO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH38RJXO.png&h=622854b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guo.media/posts/231704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guo.media%2Fposts%2F231704&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=e3e34e31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.guo.media/posts/231704</a>"},{"pid":"ead086421ad061f4d5db507d462ea47b95218dcd","tid":1548121,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T0