.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=c9404355\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到要<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>光復</strong></span>這<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>香港</strong></span><br />\n同行兒女為正義<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>時代革命</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RBK1Uyp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRBK1Uyp.jpg&h=4972b138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcMscm9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcMscm9.png&h=28084b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qOoN1Li.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqOoN1Li.jpg&h=16e8c160&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e948e11b43b18baec737ef4cfb8646f025d691ae","tid":1548121,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"917024cb9c2a80d2767128101867b6e45bdcc53f","tid":1548121,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e948e11b43b18baec737ef4cfb8646f025d691ae","tid":1548121,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"【联合国人权专员警告香港政府】<br />\n【警队执法必需符合国际人权标准】<br />\n【暴力可能急剧恶化】<br />\n联合国人权专员MICHELLE BACHELET评论香港的人权状况，她表示，已向林郑月娥提出要求，警队在应对暴力事件时，要符合国际人权法和标准。她又警告，如果香港政府未能跟民众对话，暴力事件可能会急速恶化。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1169245456997609472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRFA_Chinese%2Fstatus%2F1169245456997609472&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAQjMvzJ